Flicker/Phoenix/Pumpskin/Skyblaze::

Flicker groans and stands up, helping Phoenix to her feet.  "Always 
the worst timing."  She nods, and the two of them fly out of the base.

Pumpskin hears the comm.  "Oh, goodie!  FIGHT!!!!"  Transforming to 
beast mode, the freakish Predacon races out to confront the enemy.

Skyblaze, his body comprised entirely of energy, passes through the 
walls of the base and gets there first, letting loose a torrent of 
laser-like beams upon the bots attacking Perceptor.
